title: David Cassidy Appears Drunk In Concert | Maria Milito | 104.7 WTUE
text: David Cassidy Appears Drunk In Concert posted by Maria Milito - David Cassidy seemed drunk, slurred his words, and fell off the stage this past weekend. {"position1":{"name":"David Cassidy","id":43942,"url":"https:\/\/www.iheart.com\/artist\/david-cassidy-43942","type":"artist","errors":null,"tagged":true}} Maria Milito, a native New Yorker has been heard on the airwaves for over twenty years and loves all things rock. In 2011, Maria published Clarice and Friends...How They Helped Mend the Hole in My Heart, a collection of emails from her listeners sent to her when her beloved dog Clarice passed away and is currently working on a revised edition. A huge animal advocate, Maria can often be found at animal functions and charity events. She lives with Fredo, a black lab mix! Contact
